-- ============================================================
-- Built the way INS-ui gets its smoothness: a per-frame render loop redraws the
-- whole window from a POOLED object set, and every animated value is eased with
-- frame-rate-independent exp smoothing  v += (target-v)*(1-exp(-k*dt)). Hover,
-- the open fade+rise, eased scrolling, drag and resize all run on this. Wrapped
-- in an IIFE for a fresh 200-local register budget; only the RS data fns
-- (TakeRSSnapshot / CompareRSSnapshots / save / loadRSSnapshot) reach it as upvalues.
